      "role": "user",
      "content": "so it's basically a recycling system. but what about that feeling of it being \"disruptive\" like u said? if the body is so good at recycling it, why does it still feel like such a massive disruption to my muscles while i'm actually running? like what is actually causing the physical interference?",
      "source": "evaluator"
